feedback-privacy: Your feedback, your email address (if provided), and additional information referred to in the {privacyPolicyLinkOpen}Data Collection Policy{privacyPolicyLinkClose} will be sent to the facere team. Please do not include personal information in your feedback.
feedback-thanks: Thanks for helping us improve! We love hearing from you.
about-outline:
facere is an a VPN powered by Shadowsocks and built from Outline. 
Outline is an open source project that we modified to bring this to you. You can contribute to their code on GitHub, and follow them on Reddit and Medium.
unreachable-server-state: Unreachable | Send a feedback if you think it is blocked.
server-add-instructions: Copy and paste an access key to add a server.
server-add-invalid: {openLine}Invalid access key.{closeLine}Enter a valid access key (ss://) to add a server.
server-detected: Please confirm that you want to add this server.
server-create-your-own: Don't have an access key?{breakLine}Buy facere on {openLink}our website{closeLink}.
server-create-your-own-zero-state: Don't have an access key?{breakLine}Buy facere on {openLink}our website{closeLink}.
error-unexpected: Sorry, an unexpected error occurred. Quitting and restarting may help. If this happens again, please submit feedback.
error-timeout: Something seems to be taking longer than expected. Quitting and restarting may help. If this happens again, please submit feedback.
error-invalid-access-key: Invalid access key. Please try again, or submit feedback for help.
error-server-incompatible: Sorry, this access key is not compatible with this version of facere.
error-feedback-submission: Sorry, we were unable to submit your feedback. Please check that you are connected to the internet and try again.
outline-plugin-error-unexpected: Sorry, an unexpected error occurred. If this happens again, please submit feedback.
outline-plugin-error-vpn-permission-not-: facere needs your permission to set up a VPN connection to the server. Please try again, or submit feedback if you need help.
outline-plugin-error-invalid-server-cred: It seems like your access key is not valid. If this happens again, please contact your server admin.
outline-plugin-error-udp-forwarding-not-: It seems like this server doesn’t support UDP forwarding. If this happens again, please contact your server admin.
outline-plugin-error-server-unreachable: We can’t seem to connect to your server. Please check that you are connected to the internet and try again.
outline-plugin-error-generic-start-failu: Something happened and we couldn’t connect. If this happens again, please submit feedback.
outline-plugin-error-networking-error: A networking error occurred. If this happens again, please submit feedback.
auto-connect-dialog-detail: Unless you disconnect from your facere server, facere will automatically connect next time you restart your device.
non-system-vpn-warning-detail: Most browsers connect automatically with facere, some do not.
update-downloaded: An updated version of facere has been downloaded. It will be installed when you restart Outline.
privacy-title: facere never collects unnecessary personal information.
privacy-text: Basic information is required when you register for facere. Some technical information is sent if you submit feedback, if there's an app error or crash, or if your server administrator opts in to share anonymous server usage data.
